des:
Ask for AI Captain Facts, and learn about AI Captain on the Mayflower autonomous ship 

AI Captain Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch AI Captain Facts" or "Alexa, open AI Captain Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
